text: Hanna Anatoleuna Marusava is an archer from Belarus. Marusava competed at the 2000 Summer Olympics, the 2004 Summer Olympics, and the 2020 Summer Olympics. She was born on 8 January 1978.Hanna Karasiova-Marusava == References == Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian archers Category:Olympians for Belarus
